metadata.name: Karasuba
metadata.description:
Created by SHOKUEN.

This project is an NFT work "JUU-NIN-TO-IRO" created by 10 illustrators on the theme of "Japanese Colors".

The name of this character is "Karasuba".
The color code for Japanese colors is #180614.

She is messanger.
She is calculating and cool.
Her charm point is the wings growing out of her neck.

「Don't get too close to me or you'll get hurt.」
